replies.bodyText:
I'm curious why you need all this reflection logic. You should be able to call request.asJava() to convert the request to a Java request, so you can use all the normal Play Java API.
So below you could write:
request.asJava().attrs().getOptional(Router.Attrs.HANDLER_DEF).ifPresent(hd -> {
  span.setTag(DDTags.RESOURCE_NAME, hd.verb() + " " + hd.path());
});
It's not an immediate issue for me but I was trying to better understand how this integration works.
